RINEHART 2018-0656 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appellant's motion for relief or order pursuant to S.Ct.Prac.R. 4.01 denied. Appellee's motion to strike appellant's motion for relief or order denied. Kennedy and DeGenaro, JJ., would deny both motions as moot. DeWine, J., would deny appellee's motion to strike as moot.
